Using
-----
    rename your "*.pwn" -> "*.io.pwn" or "*.io.p" or another.
    --
    using `paw -c` to default compile mode
    --
    Before compiling, please create a data.json file in the pawnclis file area and its contents as expected, example:
    ```json
        {
            "amx_opt": "opt1 opt2 opt3 opt4 opt5 opt6..",
            "allow_subdir": "where_pawncc_and_include",
            "ppman_type": "pawnclis_package_manager_installer_type",
            "ai_token": "ai_groq_token",
            "ai_model": "ai_groq_model",
            "ai_biodata": "ai_groq_biodata",
            "ai_json_get": "ai_groq_json_get_type"
        }
    ```